---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Alternative Solutions">
    <section class="space-y-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-indigo-600 mb-3">
                Rand Water Challenge: Vandalism
            </p>
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-4">
                Alternative Solutions
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
                Our solution focuses on replacing metal parts in water meters with cheaper materials so the meters become less valuable to steal. This reduces the incentive for vandalism while keeping the system functional and cost-effective.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-6">
            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Alternative 1: Using cheaper materials</h2>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700">
            Chosen Solution
          </span>
                </div>

                <p class="text-slate-700 mb-6">
                    Use lower-cost materials for pipelines and equipment in order to reduce initial construction and maintenance costs.
                </p>

                <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
                    <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-5">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Advantages</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-slate-700">
                            <li>Lower initial investment costs.</li>
                            <li>Economically attractive in the short term.</li>
                            <li>Faster implementation due to easier material availability.</li>
                            <li>Reduced overall project budget.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-5">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Disadvantages</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-slate-700">
                            <li>Lower resistance to corrosion and potential external damage.</li>
                            <li>Shorter service life.</li>
                            <li>Higher probability of failures and leakages.</li>
                            <li>Increased long-term maintenance and repair costs.</li>
                            <li>Reduced system reliability.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Alternative 2: Deterrence and monitoring technology</h2>

                <p class="text-slate-700 mb-6">
                    Video surveillance systems, alarms and other technologies can deter vandals, but investment is required. Examples include video cameras, alarms, GPS tracking, and automatic notifications to security personnel.
                </p>

                <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
                    <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-5">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Advantages</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-slate-700">
                            <li>The solution is validated and known to work.</li>
                            <li>Effective.</li>
                            <li>Rapid incident detection.</li>
                            <li>Evidence for law enforcement.</li>
                            <li>A modern solution.</li>
                            <li>Long-term benefits.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-5">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Disadvantages</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-slate-700">
                            <li>Costly and likely unsustainable.</li>
                            <li>Requires electricity and internet.</li>
                            <li>Needs maintenance.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Alternative 3: Community-based employment for infrastructure maintenance and protection</h2>

                <p class="text-slate-700 mb-6">
                    Local job creation focused on responsibility for infrastructure maintenance and protection.
                </p>

                <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
                    <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-5">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Advantages</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-slate-700">
                            <li>Creates jobs for local residents.</li>
                            <li>Continuous infrastructure maintenance, leading to fewer failures.</li>
                            <li>Faster response to vandalism.</li>
                            <li>Reduces crime indirectly.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-5">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Disadvantages</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-slate-700">
                            <li>Permanent funding required for salaries.</li>
                            <li>May lack qualifications, so training is needed.</li>
                            <li>Does not always stop organized crime (“water mafias”).</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>
</MainLayout>